com.google.gwt.maps.client.impl
Interface InfoWindowOptionsImpl

All Superinterfaces:
JSFlyweightWrapper
@BeanProperties
public interface InfoWindowOptionsImpl
extends JSFlyweightWrapper

Provides an interface to the GInfoWindowsOptions object from the Maps API using JSIO. Note that there is no provided constructor for this object. Instead it is build from an Object literal.
